We can add up to four separate sections into our footer,

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:17.160
placing four separate pieces of content.

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:21.750
The first section over on the left and the fourth section will be over on the right.

00:00:21.750 --> 00:00:25.110
We can place inside it lots of content such as widgets.

00:00:25.110 --> 00:00:27.480
We can place menus, bestsellers,

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:32.250
top-rated products, and everything else we have access to in the widget section.

00:00:32.250 --> 00:00:38.100
