00:00:43.740 --> 00:00:47.060
We already have these menus created from the previous video.

00:00:47.060 --> 00:00:50.360
We can reuse this inside of a widget too.

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:53.975
To do this, drag over the Navigation Menu,

00:00:53.975 --> 00:00:58.645
and then select the Navigation Menu which you want to place in this location.

00:00:58.645 --> 00:01:01.710
First, User menu, Save this.

00:01:01.710 --> 00:01:04.630
We can also add our Navigation Menu too.

00:01:04.630 --> 00:01:06.830
We do this in the exact same way.

00:01:06.830 --> 00:01:14.145
Drag this over, select our second menu and then refresh the page.

00:01:14.145 --> 00:01:16.545
There's our first section.

00:01:16.545 --> 00:01:20.860
The second section, this is going to be for the address information.

00:01:20.860 --> 00:01:23.795
It's going to be a lot like our Contact Us page.

00:01:23.795 --> 00:01:27.940
Column 2. This is a text widget.

00:01:27.940 --> 00:01:30.315
Drag this into Column 2.

00:01:30.315 --> 00:01:33.735
Just like we did with the Contact Us page, the text,

00:01:33.735 --> 00:01:40.950
You can find at, and then add some sample address lines inside here.

00:01:41.450 --> 00:01:46.815
Copy. Add the same a couple more times.

00:01:46.815 --> 00:01:50.450
If you wanted to, you could also change this into a list,

00:01:50.450 --> 00:01:54.265
but I'm just going to keep this as regular text. Save this.

00:01:54.265 --> 00:01:57.960
Then just below, set up a second text block.

00:01:57.960 --> 00:02:00.075
Just like the Contact Us page,

00:02:00.075 --> 00:02:02.815
this will contain our useful contacts,

00:02:02.815 --> 00:02:07.670
the title, and then our text,

00:02:07.670 --> 00:02:10.250
which will be the email and also the URL.

00:02:10.250 --> 00:02:13.680
We can grab this from our Contact page.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:17.580
These is our two links down at the bottom.

00:02:19.060 --> 00:02:22.670
Paste this in and save this widget.

00:02:22.670 --> 00:02:24.830
We can check if this is working okay,

00:02:24.830 --> 00:02:26.705
back to the Home page.

00:02:26.705 --> 00:02:29.390
Scroll down to the footer, which is fine.

00:02:29.390 --> 00:02:32.105
Now we can move on to Column 3.

00:02:32.105 --> 00:02:34.875
Our Footer Area number 3,

00:02:34.875 --> 00:02:38.440
I'm going to drag over the Products by Rating,

00:02:38.440 --> 00:02:41.680
which is a list of all top rated products,

00:02:41.680 --> 00:02:44.405
